{"type":null,"faqId":25984,"title":"如何添加彩信附件？对附件的大小限制是多少？","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.p1{margin-left:1.18125in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n.p2{text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;keep-with-next.within-page:always;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n.p3{margin-bottom:0.027777778in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Book Antiqua;font-size:9pt;}\n.p4{margin-left:1.4409722in;margin-top:0.027777778in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:9pt;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span>在信息编辑界面，点击“</span><a name=\"gen-id1.4.4.2.1.1.1\"></a><a name=\"gen-id1.4.4.2.1.1.1\"></a><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=90627\" style=\"width:0.25in;height:0.17986111in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span>”选择您要添加的附件类型，根据屏幕提示完成添加。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>添加图片附件时，若文件过大则会自动压缩图片分辨率，再以附件形式添加到彩信中。视频或音频文件超过 300K 则无法添加为信息的附件。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<a name=\"figd0e841\"></a><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=90628\" style=\"width:2.651389in;height:3.9388888in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p  ></p>\n<p  >\n<a name=\"gen-id1.4.4.2.4\"></a><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=90629\" style=\"width:0.5in;height:0.16597222in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p class=\"p4\">\n<span>所有图片仅供参考，具体操作请以实际界面为准。</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":168,"faqType":"信息与电子邮件","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"284","faqTypeCode":"Tablet-Messaging-Emailing","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCo